<</replace>>
<</timed>>

<<timed 08s>>
  <<replace "#caption">>  
So, a lot of people, they raised funds all throughout the year. 
<</replace>>
<</timed>>

<<timed 12s>>
  <<replace "#caption">>  
So, we used to go to where Emirates Stadium was built, that was the Islington Council's transport area, 
<</replace>>
<</timed>>

<<timed 23s>>
